{"schema_version":"1","crate":"uxstrings","version":"0.9.0+alpha-20250903","id":"a890899af66b880b","name":"Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling","qualified_name":"Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling","kind":"ada_package","location":{"file":"deps/strings_edit-utf8-handling.ads","line":31,"column":9},"code":"package Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling","documentation":{"description":"\nTo_String -- Conversion from UTF-8 to Latin-1\n\n   Value        - The UTF-8 string to convert\n [ Substitute ] - For non-Latin-1 code points\n\nThese functions convert a UTF-8 encoded string to  Latin-1  character\nstring (standard Ada string). The parameter Substitute specifies  the\ncharacter  that  substitutes  non-Latin-1  code  points  in Value. If\nomitted Constraint_Error is propagated when non-Latin-1  code  points\nappear in Value. \n\nReturns :\n\n   Latin-1 equivalent\n\nExceptions :\n\n   Constraint_Error - Non-Latin-1 code points in Value\n   Data_Error       - Illegal UTF-8 string"},"subprograms":[{"id":"046b45264151cce7","name":"To_String","qualified_name":"Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling.To_String","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"deps/strings_edit-utf8-handling.ads","line":53,"column":13},"code":"function To_String (Value : String) return String"},{"id":"f3a1a67015a24961","name":"To_String","qualified_name":"Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling.To_String","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"deps/strings_edit-utf8-handling.ads","line":54,"column":13},"code":"function To_String\n         (  Value      : String;\n            Substitute : Character\n         )  return String"},{"id":"2e34aa99c13c4165","name":"To_UTF8","qualified_name":"Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling.To_UTF8","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"deps/strings_edit-utf8-handling.ads","line":73,"column":13},"code":"function To_UTF8 (Value : Character     ) return String"},{"id":"686923d7384a6c10","name":"To_UTF8","qualified_name":"Strings_Edit.UTF8.Handling.To_UTF8","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"deps/strings_edit-utf8-handli